uk.co.westhawk.test
Class SnmpTarget

java.lang.Object
  uk.co.westhawk.test.SnmpTarget
public class SnmpTarget
extends java.lang.Object

The SnmpTarget class performs tests specified according to DOM node. It is the helper class of TestSuite and TrapTestSuite.
